question: Nepali culture ko khasiyat ke ho?
response: Nepali culture diverse ani rich cha. Harek jat-jati ko aafno tradition ani festival huncha, jasle unity in diversity dekhauncha. Dashain, Tihar, Holi, ani Lhosar jastai chad sabai ko main highlight ho. Nepali le respect ko lagi elders ko aashirwad linu ani namaste garnu culture ko part ho. Folk songs, dances (jastai Tamang selo, Lakhey), ani foods (dhido, gundruk) Nepali identity ho. Art ra architecture, jastai stupas ani temples, world-famous cha.

context: Internet of Things (IoT) vaneko physical devices lai internet ko through connect garne concept ho. IoT ko examples dherai chan. Aru examples ma wearable devices jasta ki smartwatches ra fitness trackers pani parchan, jasma health data monitor garna sakincha. Industrial IoT (IIoT) ma, sensors le machinery ko performance monitor garchhan ra predictive maintenance provide garchhan. Smart cities ma, IoT le traffic management, waste management, ra energy distribution optimize garchha.
